{"tid":1636081,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"大家都立個誓好唔好","createTime":"2019-10-07T16:28:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-08T00:41:04.000Z","uid":197782,"like":17,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"df493617d39377134bd148950fb9604c27c049ce","tid":1636081,"uid":197782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T16:28:27.000Z","msg":"經過依幾日咁多悲劇，記者被歐打，少年中槍，少女被捕，車斷腳，孕婦被捕等等等等不能盡訴。<br />\n我同大家都好嬲好悲痛，會睇睇下流淚，亦同唔少人斷絕關係。但比起被捕，受傷，甚至失去性命嘅弟兄姊妹都唔算係啲咩。<br />\n <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">我在此立誓言，不論黑警或藍絲，我一世都不會原諒，今次革命，必須有狗以性命血祭</span></span><br />\n從今以後，無論手足做咩只要無違初衷，永不割蓆<br />\n不完美，可接受，可改善<br />\n兄弟爬山<br />\n光復香港，時代革命<br />\n黑警必須死<br />\n狗官永世不離大灣區"},{"pid":"99e8cc35488a7db463e04bbdcd1ab18e647ac3cd","tid":1636081,"uid":197782,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T16:35:29.000Z","msg":"記得文宣"},{"pid":"3c99d941b309cda18e8a65a4fa00dca287f9ed0f","tid":1636081,"uid":197782,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T16:35:47.000Z","msg":"今日立場記者被打"},{"pid":"b48b02de90ddc9f39c4167a7b2227cffe529f5e6","tid":1636081,"uid":197782,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T16:36:19.000Z","msg":"警察硬闖私人地方"},{"pid":"90b703082eff2fe39f58e45969e4e5d829ebd524","tid":1636081,"uid":197782,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T16:39:08.000Z","msg":"黑警藏於私家車再追捕手足"},{"pid":"5b222827cef14eae5065ea567d3791dfb2531a59","tid":1636081,"uid":328337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b48b02de90ddc9f39c4167a7b2227cffe529f5e6","tid":1636081,"uid":197782,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T16:36:19.000Z","msg":"警察硬闖私人地方"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T16:40:34.000Z","msg":"狗仔對CU記者有新邏輯<br />\n&quot;因為你部手機係黑色概 所以你係黑記&quot;<br />\n<br />\n&quot;你個口罩係黑色概 請問你係吾係黑警&quot;<br />\n食屎喇死魔警又小兒麻痺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d082d26e3f292103b8ee15ed2de2fff604ac1a57","t